# ==============================================================================
# .gitattributes — qator-oxiri (line-ending) normalizatsiyasi
# Loyiha Linux/Docker'da deploy bo'ladi → barcha matn fayllar LF.
# Bu git core.autocrlf'ni bekor qiladi va pre-commit mixed-line-ending hook
# bilan izchillikni ta'minlaydi (CRLF<->LF kurashini oldini oladi).
# ==============================================================================

# Barcha matn fayllar LF (working copy + index)
* text=auto eol=lf

# Shell skriptlar — har doim LF (Linux konteynerda bajariladi)
*.sh text eol=lf

# Binary fayllar — git eol normalizatsiyasi qilmasin
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pyc binary
